					title="GitHub"
					aria-label="GitHub"
				>
					<Icon name="mingcute:github-line" />
				</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					href="https://twitter.com/muellrxyz"
					class="group relative z-0 block w-fit rounded-full border-2 border-dotted border-transparent p-2 transition-colors duration-100 active:bg-gray-900/20 hocus:border-gray-900/20 hocus:bg-gray-900/10 dark:active:bg-gray-100/20 dark:hocus:border-gray-50/10 dark:hocus:bg-gray-100/10"
